  dialogueLines:
  - Speaker: Madame Lichenia
    Text: I noticed you before you reached me.
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: Do you say that to everyone?
  - Speaker: Madame Lichenia
    Text: No. Most people enter a room. You changed the air in it.
  - Speaker: Madame Lichenia
    Text: Sit down. Let us see what the cards make of you.
  choices:
  - choiceText: All right. Show me.
